~ create_dict
starfish: Creating a dictionary is easy!  
starfish: Use curly braces {} with key:value pairs:  
starfish: [br]hero = {'health': 100, 'mana': 50, 'level': 5}  
starfish: Notice the colon (:) between key and value!  
starfish: Create an empty dictionary:  
starfish: [br]empty_dict = {}  
starfish: ðŸ’¡ Keys are usually strings, values can be numbers, strings, lists, anything!  
