~ access_values
starfish: Accessing values is simple!  
starfish: Use square brackets [] with the key name:  
starfish: [br]hero = {'health': 100, 'mana': 50, 'level': 5}  
starfish: [br]print(hero['health'])  
starfish: This prints: 100  
starfish: âš ï¸ Warning: If the key doesn't exist, you'll get an error!  
